# Cursor Rules for Dynasty-Site2

## Repository Information
- **Repository URL:** https://github.com/blueirishfamily-hash/Dynasty-Site2.git
- **Default Branch:** main
- **Deployment:** Automatic via GitHub Pages on push to main

## Deployment Workflow

### When pushing to GitHub:
1. All changes pushed to `main` branch automatically trigger GitHub Actions deployment
2. Site deploys to: https://blueirishfamily-hash.github.io/Dynasty-Site2/
3. Deployment status can be checked in the GitHub Actions tab

### Before Committing:
- Ensure all files are saved
- Test locally if possible
- Check for any console errors

### Commit Messages:
- Use descriptive commit messages
- Format: "Brief description of changes"
- Examples:
  - "Update roster management UI"
  - "Fix dashboard API integration"
  - "Add new feature: trade analyzer"

## File Structure
- HTML files: `index.html`, `dashboard.html`, `roster.html`, `trade.html`, `draft.html`
- JavaScript: `sleeper-api.js`
- Configuration: `.gitignore`, `README.md`, `DEPLOY.md`
- Workflows: `.github/workflows/`

## Sleeper API
- League ID: 1194798912048705536
- Base URL: https://api.sleeper.app/v1
- All API calls are in `sleeper-api.js`

## Important Notes
- Never commit API keys or secrets
- Keep `.gitignore` updated
- Test changes locally before pushing
- Check GitHub Actions for deployment status

